nodes.text: A lone Gorach artist lived in a cavern in the swamps of the planet Lowick for hundreds of years. It was occasionally sighted by the native Pa'lowick, who believed the Gorach to be a legendary "swamp ape". At some point during galactic history, the Hutt hunter Parella Jiramma Baco tracked down and killed the Gorach, then dragged its corpse back to his starship.
